"content": "<h2>Sculpture created by carving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:32\">1KI 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:7\">2KI 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:17-Ezek41:18\">EZK 41:17–41:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:25\">EZK 41:25</a></p>\n<h2>Sculpture created out of metal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:23\">1KI 7:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:18\">EXO 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:24\">1KI 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:30\">1KI 7:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:37\">1KI 7:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:3\">2CH 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:2\">2CH 28:2</a></p>\n<h2>Sculpture used in the setting of idolatry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:4\">EXO 32:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24\">ACT 19:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15-Deut4:18\">DEU 4:15–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:16\">2KI 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:19–40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:12-Isa44:13\">ISA 44:12–44:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:5\">ISA 48:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:1\">DAN 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:29\">ACT 17:29</a></p>",
